  </li>
</ol>

<p>This turns the process of learning a new technology  into a <strong><em>system</em></strong> rather than a <strong>goal</strong>.Â   This is a net win because <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qKYSmrgOjp4">systems are better than goals</a>.</p>
